body:
Fixes https://github.com/grafana/grafana/issues/7627

this feature request is from Feb 2017, with a bunch of upvotes and a lot of discussion.

since it's now both possible and easy to support a symlog scale, we should either implement it or close it as WONTFIX; this PR does the former.

TODO: options UI still needs some tuning/rework

